user_query: I am starting a new programming project and I need some inspiration. Can you fetch all the programming memes from Reddit and provide me with the top quality ones? Also, search for comments on Reddit that are related to programming and have a positive sentiment. Additionally, search for posts on Reddit that have the term 'project' in the title and provide me with the post details. Finally, suggest some programming languages that are currently trending and popular.

TaskList.description: Search for comments on Reddit related to programming that have a positive sentiment.
Search for posts on Reddit that have the term 'project' in the title.
Gather details of the posts found in step 4.
Suggest trending and popular programming languages.
